1 0 0 1 0 0 cm  BT /F1 12 Tf 14.4 TL ET
BT /F2 7 Tf 8.4 TL ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 565.2756 Tm (MedTech Diagnostics | INV-2024-0067                                                    NEXUS Assembly Line Mix-up Investigation) Tj T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 556.8756 Tm  T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 548.4756 Tm  T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 540.0756 Tm  T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 531.6756 Tm  T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 523.2756 Tm (      1. Executive Summary) Tj T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 514.8756 Tm (      Investigation INV-2024-0067 was initiated following a customer complaint reporting that NEXUS Troponin kit lot) Tj T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 506.4756 Tm (      1010550120 contained sensor cartridges labelled for NEXUS CK MB. The customer identified the issue during routine kit) Tj T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 498.0756 Tm (      inspection before use. No patient results were affected.) Tj T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 489.6756 Tm (      The investigation determined that the root cause was a failure to follow the assembly line changeover procedure) Tj T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 481.2756 Tm (      \(SOP-ASM-003\). NEXUS CK MB production was followed by NEXUS Troponin on assembly line AL-003, and the) Tj T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 472.8756 Tm (      changeover was completed in only 15 minutes instead of the mandated 30-minute minimum. Residual CK MB CART) Tj T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 464.4756 Tm (      cartridges were not cleared from the feed hopper, resulting in their inclusion in Troponin kits.) Tj T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 456.0756 Tm  T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 447.6756 Tm  T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 439.2756 Tm  T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 430.8756 Tm  T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 422.4756 Tm (      2. Problem Description \(QQOCQPC\)) Tj T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 414.0756 Tm  T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 405.6756 Tm (      Qui \(Who\):) Tj T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 397.2756 Tm (      Customer site - Regional Medical Center. Assembly operator OP-045 \(J. Mitchell\) performed the changeover on) Tj T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 388.8756 Tm (      assembly line AL-003.) Tj T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 380.4756 Tm  T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 372.0756 Tm  T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 363.6756 Tm (      Quoi \(What\):) Tj T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 355.2756 Tm (      NEXUS CK MB sensor cartridges \(CART-CKMB-001\) found in NEXUS Troponin kit lot 1010550120. Approximately 48 kits in) Tj T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 346.8756 Tm (      the lot may be affected \(first production run after changeover\).) Tj T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 338.4756 Tm  T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 330.0756 Tm  T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 321.6756 Tm (      Ou \(Where\):) Tj T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 313.2756 Tm (      Assembly line AL-003, Building B, Riverside facility. Customer complaint originated from Regional Medical Center,) Tj T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 304.8756 Tm (      Riverside.) Tj T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 296.4756 Tm  T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 288.0756 Tm  T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 279.6756 Tm (      Comment \(How\):) Tj T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 271.2756 Tm (      During changeover from CK MB to Troponin production, the operator did not fully clear the sensor cartridge feed hopper.) Tj T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 262.8756 Tm (      Residual CK MB cartridges were mixed with incoming Troponin cartridges. Barcode scanner was in bypass mode due to an) Tj T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 254.4756 Tm (      earlier scanner fault \(STOP-2024-0015\).) Tj T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 246.0756 Tm  T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 237.6756 Tm  T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 229.2756 Tm (      Quand \(When\):) Tj T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 220.8756 Tm (      Changeover occurred on 2024-03-05 at 14:30. Production of Troponin lot 1010550120 started at 14:45 \(only 15) Tj T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 212.4756 Tm (      minutes after changeover vs. 30-minute minimum per SOP-ASM-003\). Customer complaint received: 2024-03-10.) Tj T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 204.0756 Tm  T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 195.6756 Tm  T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 187.2756 Tm (      Pourquoi \(Why\):) Tj T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 178.8756 Tm (      Operator rushed the changeover due to production schedule pressure. The 8-item clearance checklist was signed but) Tj T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 170.4756 Tm (      items 3 \(hopper clearance\) and 6 \(barcode scanner verification\) were not actually performed.) Tj T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 162.0756 Tm  T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 153.6756 Tm  T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 145.2756 Tm (      Combien \(How much\):) Tj T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 136.8756 Tm (      1 lot affected \(1010550120, ~2,500 kits\). Voluntary recall of entire lot. Estimated cost: 45,000 EUR \(recall +) Tj T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 128.4756 Tm (      investigation + replacement production\). No patient harm reported.) Tj T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 120.0756 Tm  T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 111.6756 Tm  T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 103.2756 Tm  T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 94.87559 Tm  T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 86.47559 Tm (      3. Data Analysis) Tj T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 78.07559 Tm  T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 69.67559 Tm (      3.1 Production Chronology) Tj T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 61.27559 Tm  T* ET
 
