BT 1 0 0 1 30 220.8756 Tm  T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 212.4756 Tm (      3.3 Equipment Review) Tj T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 204.0756 Tm (      Assembly line AL-003 mechanical inspection showed no equipment faults. However, the barcode scanner \(BC-003\)) Tj T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 195.6756 Tm (      was in bypass mode since 2024-03-03 due to a communication fault \(STOP-2024-0015\). A repair request had been) Tj T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 187.2756 Tm (      submitted but was pending maintenance scheduling. With the scanner in bypass, automatic rejection of mismatched) Tj T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 178.8756 Tm (      sensor cartridges was disabled.) Tj T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 170.4756 Tm  T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 162.0756 Tm  T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 153.6756 Tm  T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 145.2756 Tm  T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 136.8756 Tm (      4. Root Cause Analysis) Tj T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 128.4756 Tm (      Root Cause: Changeover procedure \(SOP-ASM-003\) not followed. Operator did not clear sensor cartridge hopper and did) Tj T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 120.0756 Tm (      not verify barcode scanner operation. Changeover completed in 15 minutes vs. 30-minute minimum requirement.) Tj T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 111.6756 Tm (      5M Category: Methode \(Method\) / Process) Tj T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 103.2756 Tm (      Contributing Factors:) Tj T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 94.87559 Tm (      - Production schedule pressure: two product changeovers in one day.) Tj T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 86.47559 Tm (      - Barcode scanner in bypass mode \(STOP-2024-0015\), disabling automatic detection.) Tj T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 78.07559 Tm (      - Supervisor sign-off \(checklist item 8\) was not enforced.) Tj T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 69.67559 Tm (      - No physical interlock to prevent production start with incomplete changeover.) Tj T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 61.27559 Tm  T* ET
 
